                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420131-811-offence-1 t18420131-cd-198"></join>24th of January</rs>, 1141bs. weight of white lead, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; 20 printed books, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 box, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18420131-name-1184" type="victimName">
